    "name": "Claude",
    "epitet": "The Schemer",
    "display": "Claude: The Schemer",
    "description": "Heir to House Riegan, the leading house of the Leicester Alliance. Employs both an easygoing attitude and an effortless skill for scheming. Appears in Fire Emblem: Three Houses.",
    "artist": "Sata (沙汰)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Joe Zieja",
    "voiceActorJP": "豊永利行",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I'm Claude. I'm not big on formalities, so no need to put on airs. Feel free to throw me a feast any time, though.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'm not thrilled about how I got here, but seeing folks from different worlds work together like this? It's nice.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Someday I'll lead the Leicester Alliance, but my ambitions are far grander. I want to change the world.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I like you. If you want something, you don't just pray for it—you take action. We have that in common.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Everyone here takes themselves so seriously. Why don't we have a feast? That would lighten things up.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I've been mixing up a new poison. Some might call it a dirty trick, but I just like to come prepared.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I was asked to say hello by <Friend Name>, so... Hello! And with that, I'll be off.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "Sometimes I even surprise myself.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I expected as much.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Not one of my finer moments.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'll put this power to good use.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "I didn't plan on staying here this long. Time flies, I guess. Sometimes I wish I could leave, but then I think about... You. There's something about you. You have a presence that compels people to follow you—me included. I've never been much of a follower, but you make me so curious, I can't help but stay by your side. I'll go back to my world someday. Before that happens, though, I want to learn more about you. So I'm planning to stick close to you from now on. That won't be an issue, right? I'm a useful guy to have around.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
